            I listened with great interest to what the Minister said in reply and I thank him for the details of the education figures. I know that he and his colleagues
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_370gc' title='Col. 370GC &mdash; HL Deb 18 July 2002 vol 637 c370GC' name='column_370gc' href='#column_370gc' rel='bookmark'>370GC</a>
