      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0637P0-04990'>
        <a name='S5LV0637P0_20020718_GCR_96'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-philip-hunt' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0637P0_20020718_GCR_96' title='Link to this speech by Mr Philip Hunt' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
